  <brief_title>Observational Study in Type 2 Diabetics Failing on Oral Antidiabetic Therapy and Starting on Insulin Treatment</brief_title>
  <acronym>HA-BOT</acronym>
  <official_title>Observational Study of Glycaemic Control in Type 2 Diabetic Patients Uncontrolled on Oral Antidiabetic Agents and Starting With Once Daily Levemir® (Insulin Detemir) - 24 Weeks, Prospective, Multicentre Observational Study in Hungary</official_title>
