  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Europe. The aim of this observational study is to evaluate
      glycaemic control in subjects with type 2 diabetes using once daily Levemir® as initiation of
      insulin therapy in Hungary.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
